{"tid":2494231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咁連登仔連登仔喺度地圖炮嗰班真係好撚煩","createTime":"2021-04-18T13:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T13:42:06.000Z","uid":360404,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"27ef683b2215fd09209225a0848a1982232c32ed","tid":2494231,"uid":360404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:11:16.000Z","msg":"成日自己想講既野就一野屈尻哂全部會員<br />\n明明自己都上連登，一野屌尻哂全部係咪顯得自己特別優越？<br />\n就係呢類人所以連登個討論風氣先會咁差<br />\n會將咁多人generalise做一個個體既人多數都弱弱地智<br />\n佢地係咪覺得金鐘嗰班毒撚=所有連登會員？<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲霧號真係用得好撚柒，成日格硬塞啲人哋冇講過嘅說話落人嘅把口度，真心同中國啲小粉紅冇分別，次次上親連登見親呢啲戇尻仔就燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係呢啲戇尻仔係block極都仲有"},{"pid":"e36e74f3c2d127e9600566a033d0aa0c9e092a19","tid":2494231,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:17:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"></span>"},{"pid":"6f1a3d66b91e584750fbd5ca9937189d62255a27","tid":2494231,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"只要你無對號入座咁就得"},{"pid":"bd25e9c18e1a40b863c077e529acd4f286f6b5fb","tid":2494231,"uid":360404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6f1a3d66b91e584750fbd5ca9937189d62255a27","tid":2494231,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"只要你無對號入座咁就得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:29:09.000Z","msg":"咁我有時候留言，有啲戇尻仔係直接quote我個comment話「連登仔又話乜乜乜，依加又點點點」<br />\n呢啲係擺明屈尻你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲野明明自己根本都冇講過，佢地係將其他會員講嘅嘢入你數"},{"pid":"8fd00bd6674152a42af5ddae674d59d537f628ac","tid":2494231,"uid":162539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bd25e9c18e1a40b863c077e529acd4f286f6b5fb","tid":2494231,"uid":360404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6f1a3d66b91e584750fbd5ca9937189d62255a27","tid":2494231,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"只要你無對號入座咁就得"},"citedBy":2,"reply